OL,3,CTwo women charged after videos of
OL,4,Ctoddler vaping shared online
OL,6,FTwo women have been charged after
OL,7,Fvideos of a toddler vaping were posted
OL,8,Fon social media.
OL,10,FPolice said the infant involved is
OL,11,F"safe and well".
OL,13,Freported the footage filmed in
OL,14,FAyrshire showed a toddler, thought to
OL,15,Fbe aged between one and two, inhaling
OL,16,Ffrom a pink vape as adults watch.
OL,18,FAnother video showed the youngster
OL,19,Fcoughing after using the vape. Police
OL,20,FScotland said two 19-year-old women
OL,21,Fwere charged on Saturday.
