OL,6,FA Police Scotland spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Two women, both aged 19 years, are
OL,8,Fthe subject of a report to the
OL,9,Fprocurator fiscal. The child is safe
OL,10,Fand well."
OL,12,FAyrshire MSP Siobhian Brown told the
OL,13,Fnewspaper she was "horrified" by the
OL,14,Ffootage.
