OL,6,FThe SNP MSP, who is also the Scottish
OL,7,Fcommunity safety minister, said: "I
OL,8,Fwas horrified to watch the footage of
OL,9,Fa toddler vaping on social media.
OL,10,FVapes are not harmless and contain
OL,11,Fnicotine and dangerous toxins that
OL,12,Fcould damage young developing lungs.
OL,14,F"I would hope this is an isolated
OL,15,Fincident and most responsible parents
OL,16,Fwould know the dangers involved.
