OL,4,Ctoddler vaping shared online
OL,6,F"I have had concerns for several years
OL,7,Fwith the increase of youth vaping,
OL,8,Fespecially with the attractive
OL,9,Fdifferent flavours and the
OL,10,Faccessibility of disposable vapes. The
OL,11,FScottish Government is bringing in
OL,12,Fwelcome legislation to ban disposable
OL,13,Fvapes next year."
OL,15,FSheila Duffy, chief executive of
OL,16,Fcharity Action on Smoking and Health
OL,17,F(Ash) Scotland, said: "Most e-
OL,18,Fcigarettes contain high levels of
OL,19,Fnicotine as well as toxic chemicals
OL,20,Fthat have not been safety tested for
OL,21,Finhalation.
