OL,6,F"E-cigarettes present particular risks
OL,7,Ffor children and all vaping products
OL,8,Fshould be kept out of their reach.
OL,10,F"Nicotine is addictive and adversely
OL,11,Faffects brain development. It can lead
OL,12,Fto attention disorders and can harm
OL,13,Fmood and wellbeing.
OL,15,F"As children's bodies are growing,
OL,16,Fdamage done by these devices now
OL,17,Fincreases the risk of serious longer-
OL,18,Fterm health outcomes."
